      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner plates. Recent mechanical service includes a VANOS overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment (Shim service). The suspension is sorted with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, providing precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While the Titan Silver finish shows minor rock chips consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains robust and the rod bearings have been inspected. A true driver's spec for the discerning purist.",
